\begin_layout Standard
כלומר,
 מתקיים:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\expectedValue\left(X\right)=\sum_{x\in\real}x\cdot\probability\left(X=x\right)\exeq{Supp\left(\probability\right)=\natural}\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}n\cdot\probability\left(X=n\right)=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}n\cdot\left(1-p\right)^{n-1}\cdot p=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{n}{2^{n}}=\frac{1}{2}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
נניח כי בשלילה 
\begin_inset Formula $\expectedValue\left(X^{2}\right)$
\end_inset

